PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR, namely the Hon. T. ALEXANDER HICKMAN, Chief Justice (Trial Division) of the Supreme Court of Newfoundland, who shall temporarily execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of NEWFOUNDLAND for the duration of the period extending from November 5 to November 6, 1993.
